&lt;p style=&quot;font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt; 
&lt;p style=&quot;font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;The PCI Security Standards Council (PCI SSC) has published a &lt;em&gt;Mobile Payments on Commercial Off-The-Shelf (MPoC) Guidance Document&lt;/em&gt;, a new resource developed to support consistent interpretation and implementation of the MPoC Standard and Program requirements across the mobile payments ecosystem. &lt;/p&gt;
